<h2>Why SEO Matters for Electricians</h2>
<p>Electrical work is an emergency-driven industry. A homeowner with a tripped breaker at 10 PM does not flip through a phone book. They grab their phone and search. 97% of consumers use online search to find local services (<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/local-seo-stats">HubSpot</a>).</p>
<p>The electrician who ranks first gets the call. Everyone else gets nothing.</p>
