<h3>Why Electricians Are Uniquely Positioned</h3>
<p>Electrical work has traits that make SEO especially effective. Emergency searches convert faster than almost any other home service. Service calls have high ticket values. Repeat customers are common for commercial electricians. And most electrical contractors have weak online presences, which means less competition.</p>
<p><a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/local-seo-stats">46% of all Google searches have local intent</a>. For electricians, that percentage is even higher. Nobody searches for an electrician 3 states away. Every search is local. Every click is a potential booked job.</p>
