<h3>How to Find Your Local Keywords</h3>
<p>Start with <a href="/blog/keyword-research-for-blog-posts/">keyword research</a> specific to your service area. Combine service type + city for every page you build.</p>
<p>A master electrician in Phoenix should target:</p>
<ul>
